OL,7,FA new report into social isolation
OL,8,Famong Worthing's elderly community has
OL,9,Frevealed shocking findings.
OL,11,FThe Guild Care charity says people who
OL,12,Fare lonely are twice as likely to
OL,13,Fsuffer from dementia, three times more
OL,14,Flikely to develop depression.
OL,16,FTo combat the problem, they run
OL,17,Fcommunity support classes but they are
OL,18,Fstruggling to cope with the demand for
OL,19,Fthem.
