OL,7,FWorthing has an ageing population. The
OL,8,F2021 census revealed there are 111,400
OL,9,Fpeople living in the town and 24,900
OL,10,Fof these are aged 65 or over.
OL,12,FThis is an increase of 15.4% in the
OL,13,Flast ten years, and 22% of the total
OL,14,Fpopulation of the town as a whole.
OL,16,FTo help ease the problem of social
OL,17,Fisolation and loneliness, the charity
OL,18,Fruns a network of classes and
OL,19,Ftransportation for pensioners.
