OL,7,FBut bingo sessions, sing-along
OL,8,Fclasses, lunches and teas are proving
OL,9,Fso popular they're now over-subscribed
OL,10,Fwith around 200 attending each week.
OL,12,F"The impact of social isolation can be
OL,13,Fhorrendous," CEO Alex brooks-Johnson
OL,14,Fsaid. "And I think it's a growing
OL,15,Fissue and becoming a national problem
OL,16,Fof significant proportion.
