OL,7,F"We know that people that are in
OL,8,Fsocial isolation, and older people
OL,9,Fespecially, are more likely to visit
OL,10,Ftheir GP, more likely to be admitted
OL,11,Fto hospital.
OL,13,F"In fact the health impact has been
OL,14,Fequated to smoking 15 cigarettes a
OL,15,Fday."
OL,17,F"I lost my wife five years ago and so
OL,18,FI broke down quite a bit," pensioner
OL,19,FJohn Kirsten added.
