OL,7,F"I don't think anybody realises it
OL,8,Funtil it happens to them what it's
OL,9,Flike, you know, to be alone and not
OL,10,Fhave your partner with you.
OL,12,F"I do this to mix with people so that
OL,13,FI can get out and often you come in
OL,14,Fand you're feeling a bit low and when
OL,15,Fyou walk out, you feel great."
