OL,7,F"There are so many people out there
OL,8,Fnow that we've had to give up some of
OL,9,Four days to let these new people come
OL,10,Fin because the rooms aren't big
OL,11,Fenough," 86 year old Shirley Craig
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I don't like giving up my day, I
OL,15,Fdon't know what to do otherwise."
OL,17,FThe charity said 83% of people asked,
OL,18,Ffeel less lonely since joining in with
OL,19,Fthe sessions, many of which are free
OL,20,Fand run by volunteers.
